# Entity tabs (`EntityTabsComponent`)

Shared sticky tab bar for user portal **Find** (`/find`) and **Our listings** (`/our-listings`) hub pages.

## Component

| Path | Selector | Role |
|------|----------|------|
| `shared/ui/entity-tabs/` | `app-entity-tabs` | Pill tabs with Lucide icon + label |

### API

| Input / output | Type |
|----------------|------|
| `activeTab` | `UserEntityTab` (`transport` \| `freight` \| `warehouse`) |
| `tabs` | `EntityTabConfig[]` — `{ id, labelKey, icon }` |
| `tabChange` | output `UserEntityTab` |

Tab config: `portal/user/user-entity-tabs.config.ts` → `USER_ENTITY_TAB_CONFIG` (icons from `UserPageIcons`).

### i18n

`portal.user.features.entityTabs.transport|freight|warehouse` + `…entityTabs.ariaLabel`

## URL convention

| Constant | Path |
|----------|------|
| `USER_FIND_URL` | `/find` |
| `USER_OUR_LISTINGS_URL` | `/our-listings` |
| `userFindUrl(tab?)` | `/find?tab=transport` — use with `navigateByUrl()` only |
| `userOurListingsUrl(tab?)` | `/our-listings?tab=transport` — use with `navigateByUrl()` only |
| `userFindRoute(tab?)` | `{ route, queryParams }` — use with `[routerLink]` + `[queryParams]` |
| `userOurListingsRoute(tab?)` | `{ route, queryParams }` — use with `[routerLink]` + `[queryParams]` |

Parse query with `parseUserEntityTab()` from `shared/constants/user-urls.ts`.

Hub pages subscribe to `ActivatedRoute.queryParamMap` and navigate with `userFindUrl()` / `userOurListingsUrl()` on tab change (programmatic navigation).

For `[routerLink]` in templates, use `userFindRoute()` / `userOurListingsRoute()` — `{ route, queryParams }`. Do **not** bind `userFindUrl()` strings to `routerLink` (Angular encodes `?` into the path segment).

Sidebar hub links stay active with `?tab=` via `navLinkActiveOptions()` in `portal/common/utils/nav-link-active-options.ts` — see `layout.mdc`.

## Hub pages

| Feature | Route | Title keys | Table body |
|---------|-------|------------|------------|
| `features/find/` | `/find` | `pages.find.*` | Embedded `*AllTablePageComponent` with `[embedded]="true"` — no create CTA |
| `features/our-listings/` | `/our-listings` | `pages.ourListings.*` | Embedded `*OurTablePageComponent` with `[embedded]="true"`; hub header owns tab-specific `PrimaryActionLink` |

List tables stay in feature `table-all/` / `table-our/` folders — **not** standalone routes in Plan 3.

## Embedded table pages

Marketplace and our table page components accept `embedded = input(false)`. When `true`, skip `PageTitleComponent` / `PageHeaderComponent` chrome; render `DataTableComponent` only.

## Sidebar (Plan 3)

Four flat clickable sections in `USER_NAV` — Home, Find, Our listings, Offer (`NavSection.route`; no nested items). See `layout.mdc`.

## Do not

- Register standalone `/transport`, `/freight`, `/warehouse`, or `*/our` list routes alongside hubs.
- Hardcode `/find?tab=` strings — use `userFindUrl()` / `userOurListingsUrl()`.
